headline.main: CATHOLIC EPISCOPAL COUNCIL.; Interesting Ceremonies. Third and Last Solemn Session. SERMON OF BISHOP M'CLOSKEY.

docs.lead_paragraph: The concluding public session of the Provincial Council of Roman Catholic Prelates and Theologians, now assembled in this City, was celebrated yesterday (Sunday) in the Metropolitan Church, corner of Mott and Prince-streets.
